trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" /> types to UI Automation.
The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabControlAutomationPeer" /> that is the parent of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" /> class.
Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" />에 연결된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />의 컨트롤 형식을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType" />.
The <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.TabItem" /> enumeration value.
Gets the collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" />에 연결된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />의 자식 요소 컬렉션을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren" />.
The collection of child elements.
Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />.
Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.
A string that contains "TabItem".
Gets the text label of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TabItemAutomationPeer" />와 연결된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TabItem" />의 텍스트 레이블을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetName" />.
The string that contains the label.

If set, this method returns the value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.Name" /> property; otherwise this method will return the value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header" /> property.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.Name" /> 속성이 설정된 경우 이 메서드는 이 속성의 값을 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header" /> 속성의 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The name property can be thought of as the string of text that a user would use to explain which control is being referred to.
trans-unit.target: Name 속성은 사용자가 참조 되는 컨트롤을 설명 하기 위해 사용 하는 텍스트 문자열으로 생각할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: It is important to have a textual representation for all controls in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/includes/tlasharptla-gui-md.md)] so that you can programmatically refer to the control in a localized manner.
trans-unit.target: 모든 컨트롤에 대 한 텍스트 표현이 해야는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/includes/tlasharptla-gui-md.md)] 지역화 된 방식으로 컨트롤을 프로그래밍 방식으로 참조할 수 있도록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: This type or member supports the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)] infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 이 형식 또는 멤버는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)] 인프라를 지원하며 사용자 코드에서 직접 사용할 수 없습니다.
